## Conventions
Governance rules live in `.claude/rules/` (decision-log, frontmatter, publishing,
hours). Dynamic-workflow harnesses live in `.claude/skills/` — run `decision-audit`
before a close-out, `scope-creep` before a scope conversation, and
`weekly-synthesis` at sprint boundaries. Harnesses that synthesize are
rubric-gated (`.claude/rubrics/`): an independent verifier grades the output and
the harness self-corrects until the rubric passes or its budget is spent.

## Team Brain
If `aios.yaml` has a `brain_url`, this repo syncs tier-tagged content to the AIOS
Team Brain. Use the `aios-sync` skill (or `aios status|push|pull|query` directly).
`access: admin` content and untagged files never sync — promotion is deliberate.

